a-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58800209&h=cbbce9d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181016/58800209</a><br />\n<br />\n批個廁所都批成世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，被問到西九龍高鐵站巴士總站為何站內沒有洗手間供巴士司機使用，而司機由巴士站行到附近洗手間需10分鐘，九巴則申請4個化學廁所於站內。運輸署代表指，未能短時間內興建廁所，故於9月28日已批准化學廁所的申請。倫明高則質疑，為何在設計巴士站時沒有考慮加裝洗手間，批評這明顯是制度問題，沒有理由事後才批准申請廁所事宜。</span><br />\n<br />\n巴士司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d24fe13ec88068ba5f3e7cb8fae4f406180d648","tid":866614,"uid":154901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:24:48.000Z","msg":"跟本起個站都係為左高鐵班人 邊理得你班巴士佬咁多"},{"pid":"b3e3d55a5d41e57b571f62040a02171dd4328b9c","tid":866614,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"何止冇用<br />\n直情有反作用"},{"pid":"5509fca7b73da890dcbc9db71f04f23f328138e4","tid":866614,"uid":133806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"33309ac2bacdf27c62596e8aba2cf14b7711e4fb","tid":866614,"uid":62532,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:12:04.000Z","msg":"TD除左問路之外 冇其他作用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n發車牌俾啲弱智周街撞囉"},{"pid":"8834b5ee66816761b6e8f68bf9a3421fd387cb8b","tid":866614,"uid":154803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"96d19ef4cd30a78de9389b8c63647e66049a0d05","tid":866614,"uid":154958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"【巴士聽證會】車站無預設廁所予司機 倫明高：明顯是制度問題<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181016/58800209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58800209&d=MhuHPZVxdG7nVaFusxlDhP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5e6a8a0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58800209&h=cbbce9d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181016/58800209</a><br />\n<br />\n批個廁所都批成世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:54:13.000Z","msg":"運吉:行十分鐘咪有廁所 你嫌遠咋麻 唔關我事"},{"pid":"5c772b09b2c0a387a049ca36d21a6e789bf3a280","tid":866614,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"康文署  食環署  頭兩名"},{"pid":"f2e6e3e07a3ef0fdb886eb033b610c12619d7f6e","tid":866614,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"TD多做多錯，少做少錯，唔做唔錯"},{"pid":"f41050b1ae82270dbc34ead0770194be859f0aa6","tid":866614,"uid":30647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"之前 9 月 12日嘅新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n運輸署 話九巴失實陳述<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n高鐵西九龍巴士站有廁所 運輸署：對九巴失實陳述感遺憾<br />\n<br />\n巴士服務獨立檢討委員會聽證會上，九巴副車務總監彭樹雄指，不明白為何部分近年落成的新巴士車站沒有廁所及休息室，對規劃感到驚奇。而且高鐵巴士總站及紅鸞道車站，設計未能兼容新款長巴士，認為落成後要大幅修改車站。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">運輸署傍晚回覆指，西九龍站巴士總站已設有一個公共洗手間，而九巴及城巴均已設置站長室及員工休息室，對於彭樹雄失實陳述表示遺憾。</span>另外，運輸署與九巴及城巴較早前已安排巴士在巴士總站試行，已完成改動相關路面設施工程，以配合該巴士總站於9月16日啟用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%AB%99%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80-%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E7%BD%B2-%E5%B0%8D%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%A4%B1%E5%AF%A6%E9%99%B3%E8%BF%B0%E6%84%9F%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE-115900027.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%2589%2580-%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B9%2